{"tid":1324714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求証]  插眼/按眼係咪警察學堂有教既招數？","createTime":"2019-07-16T15:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T00:39:48.000Z","uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"950dca36698f018e16882efe5c637ec8ed87e8ca","tid":1324714,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:44:37.000Z","msg":"有條友，我懷疑佢係低能仔，佢話制伏人既其中一招就是按眼，之前睇軍人訓練已經見過；佢有同事做過警察，亦向佢確認學堂有教呢招。<br />\n<br />\n所以我想問，警察係咪真係有教呢招？<br />\n我極度懷疑既係：<br />\n1. 插眼/按眼，當時人痛，又危險，就自然會更加意圖掙開(自然反應)。咁點可以用來制服人？？<br />\n2. 唔小心會眼盲"},{"pid":"66f7aebef554346c30cea7c3951fc42b3afca38c","tid":1324714,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T21:26:33.000Z","msg":"有無人知？"},{"pid":"b5de123078542d670d41fcbf7cdca7b82c4c1cfd","tid":1324714,"uid":238973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T21:29:09.000Z","msg":"只係知道係容易被人咬斷指既招數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d95270af37b88f5a88e5a9daadad69a9fa8a0138","tid":1324714,"uid":264806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T00:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}